Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:1.3":{"pli":"Samādānahetuko phasso vaḍḍhati, vedanā vaḍḍhati, saññā vaḍḍhati, cetanā vaḍḍhati, cittaṁ vaḍḍhati, saddhā vaḍḍhati, vīriyaṁ vaḍḍhati, sati vaḍḍhati, samādhi vaḍḍhati, paññā vaḍḍhatīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:1.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv10.9:2.1":{"pli":"Samādānahetukaṁ sīlaṁ vaḍḍhatīti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv10.9:2.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:2.3":{"pli":"Latā viya vaḍḍhati, māluvā viya vaḍḍhati, rukkho viya vaḍḍhati, tiṇaṁ viya vaḍḍhati, muñjapuñjo viya vaḍḍhatīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:2.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv10.9:3.1":{"pli":"Samādānahetukaṁ sīlaṁ vaḍḍhatīti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv10.9:3.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:3.3":{"pli":"Sīlaṁ samādiyitvā kāmavitakkaṁ vitakkentassa byāpādavitakkaṁ vitakkentassa vihiṁsāvitakkaṁ vitakkentassa sīlaṁ vaḍḍhatīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:3.4":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:3.5":{"pli":"Dvinnaṁ phassānaṁ …pe… dvinnaṁ cittānaṁ samodhānaṁ hotīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:3.6":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… dvinnaṁ phassānaṁ …pe… dvinnaṁ cittānaṁ samodhānaṁ hotīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:3.7":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:3.8":{"pli":"Kusalākusalā sāvajjānavajjā hīnapaṇītā kaṇhasukkasappaṭibhāgā dhammā sammukhībhāvaṁ āgacchantīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:3.9":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv10.9:4.1":{"pli":"Kusalākusalā sāvajjānavajjā hīnapaṇītā kaṇhasukkasappaṭibhāgā dhammā sammukhībhāvaṁ āgacchantīti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv10.9:4.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:4.3":{"pli":"Nanu vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:4.4":{"pli":"“cattārimāni, bhikkhave, suvidūravidūrāni. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:4.5":{"pli":"Katamāni cattāri? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:4.6":{"pli":"Nabhañca, bhikkhave, pathavī ca—","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:4.7":{"pli":"idaṁ paṭhamaṁ suvidūravidūraṁ …pe… tasmā sataṁ dhammo asabbhi ārakā”ti. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:4.8":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:4.9":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:4.10":{"pli":"Tena hi na vattabbaṁ—","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:4.11":{"pli":"“kusalākusalā sāvajjānavajjā hīnapaṇītā kaṇhasukkasappaṭibhāgā dhammā sammukhībhāvaṁ āgacchantī”ti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv10.9:5.1":{"pli":"Na vattabbaṁ—","html":"<p data-doxy='heterodox'>{}"},"kv10.9:5.2":{"pli":"“samādānahetukaṁ sīlaṁ vaḍḍhatī”ti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:5.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:5.4":{"pli":"Nanu vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:5.5":{"pli":"“ārāmaropā vanaropā …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:5.6":{"pli":"dhammaṭṭhā sīlasampannā te janā saggagāmino”ti. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:5.7":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:5.8":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.9:5.9":{"pli":"Tena hi samādānahetukaṁ sīlaṁ vaḍḍhatīti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv10.9:5.10":{"pli":"Samādānahetukathā niṭṭhitā. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"kv11.1":{"kv11.1:0.1":{"pli":"Kathāvatthu ","html":"<article id='kv11.1'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"kv11.1:0.2":{"pli":"Anusayapaṇṇāsaka ","html":"<li>{}</li>"},"kv11.1:0.3":{"pli":"Ekādasamavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"kv11.1:0.4":{"pli":"Tissopianusayakathā ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"kv11.1:1.1":{"pli":"Anusayā abyākatāti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv11.1:1.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv11.1:1.3":{"pli":"Vipākābyākatā kiriyābyākatā rūpaṁ nibbānaṁ cakkhāyatanaṁ …pe… phoṭṭhabbāyatananti? ","html":"{}"},"kv11.1:1.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv11.1:2.1":{"pli":"Kāmarāgānusayo abyākatoti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv11.1:2.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv11.1:2.3":{"pli":"Kāmarāgo kāmarāgapariyuṭṭhānaṁ kāmarāgasaṁyojanaṁ kāmogho kāmayogo kāmacchandanīvaraṇaṁ abyākatanti? ","html":"{}"},"kv11.1:2.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv11.1:2.5":{"pli":"kāmarāgo 